    "name": "Fungal Exhalation",
    "rank": 3,
    "spell_type": "focus",
    "subtype": "spell",
    "text": "You exhale toxic mold spores that fill the area. You deal 6d4 poison damage to creatures in the area. On a failure, a creature is also sickened 1, or sickened 2 on a critical failure. A creature that doesn\u2019t breathe is immune to this effect.",
